application.pane

Interface PaneReplacerShortened

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PaneReplacer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaFXAppController

    public interface PaneReplacerShortened
extends PaneReplacer
    This interface serves a Class that has a BorderPane as a field.

    This interface is used to simplify the call to the PaneReplacer.setPane(BorderPane, Pane, String) method, to make the calls to it shorter.
